---
title: One-Pan Chicken Sausage Tortelloni Bake with a Crispy Parmesan Panko Topping
description: Think a cheesy stuffed pasta can’t get any better? What about baking it in a creamy sauce with a crispy topping? In this recipe, we toss cheese-stuffed tortelloni in an herby tomato cream sauce, then top with Parmesan and panko breadcrumbs. Once broiled, it turns into a showstopping topping that’ll earn you plenty of oohs and aahs from your lucky fellow diners.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/63f4d66d8877805e4b01e49b-66a31f0c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/646e4594e2c35e1193e01ce4.pdf
